{
  "stem": "8569.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was having his lunch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was cutting a piece of black bread-- we haven't seen bread for a while-- and gave it to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I turned my back to him and went back to join Isabela, not as a Jewish girl, but as a Polish girl who would not take bread from an enemy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very much discussed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older sister had a private tutor, who then became her husband eventually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a student at the Warsaw University.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mieczyslaw Zeielinski.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want me to spell it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It is M-I-E-C-Z-Y-S-L-A-W, capital Z-E-I-E-L-I-N-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was studying to be a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, as a student at the university, there was a great deal of talk about Hitler and Germany and whether there will be a war or there won't be a war and what is happening.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think at that time-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] just prior to the war, the preoccupation was that German would probably declare war on Poland and the Poles were invincible, they are going to defend themselves.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, he was not seen, at least in our eyes, as a big threat, Polish versus Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did know, of course, that there were-- that there was prosecution and persecution of Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because many of the Jews were thrown out of Germany and came into Warsaw, and we used to meet some of them who were immigrants from Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew what was going on in terms of Jews, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew Hitler's antisemitic remarks and persecution of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we knew that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time-- it depends when we're talking about.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
